  • Reference

    Quantile functions for functional time series

    quantile.fts.Rd

    Computes quantiles of functional time series at each variable.

    # S3 method for class 'fts'
quantile(x, probs, ...)

    Arguments

    x

    An object of class fts.

    probs

    Quantile percentages.

    ...

    Other arguments.

    Value

    Return quantiles for each variable.

    Author

    Han Lin Shang

    See also

    mean.fts, median.fts, var.fts, sd.fts

    Examples

    quantile(x = ElNino_ERSST_region_1and2)
#>       0%   25%   50%   75%  100%
#> 1  22.66 23.79 24.19 24.56 28.12
#> 2  24.32 25.35 25.70 26.20 28.74
#> 3  24.36 25.62 26.02 26.65 29.23
#> 4  22.45 24.43 25.12 25.94 28.86
#> 5  21.43 23.17 23.85 24.90 28.26
#> 6  20.66 21.85 22.40 23.68 27.36
#> 7  19.13 20.93 21.46 22.24 25.76
#> 8  19.16 19.98 20.60 21.25 24.96
#> 9  18.92 19.74 20.43 21.10 24.69
#> 10 18.98 19.99 20.54 21.37 24.69
#> 11 19.41 20.70 21.37 22.05 26.12
#> 12 20.93 21.89 22.41 23.18 27.06
